# Authentication Endpoints

### Login
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "gilmar.ribeiro.santana@gmail.com",
  "password": "Senha.123"
}

###

### Refresh Token
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "accessToken": "{{JWT_Token}}",
  "refreshToken": "{{login.response.body.$.refreshToken}}"
}

###

### Logout
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

###

# User Endpoints (Require Authentication)

### Get All Users
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/Users?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

###

### Get User by ID
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/Users/{{login.response.body.$.userId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

###

### Create User
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "userName": "newuser",
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "NewUser123!",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890"
}

###

### Update User
PUT {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Users/{{login.response.body.$.userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "userName": "updateduser",
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+9876543210"
}

###

### Delete User
DELETE {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Users/{{login.response.body.$.userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

###

# Role Endpoints (Require Authentication)

### Get All Roles
GET {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Roles
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

###

### Create Role
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Roles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "name": "Admin",
  "description": "Administrator role"
}

###

# Claims Endpoints (Require Authentication)

### Add Claim to User
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Claims/add-to-user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "userId": "{{login.response.body.$.userId}}",
  "claimType": "permission",
  "claimValue": "read_users"
}

###

### Remove Claim from User
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Claims/remove-from-user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "userId": "{{login.response.body.$.userId}}",
  "claimType": "permission",
  "claimValue": "read_users"
}

###

# Token Endpoints (Require Authentication)

### Generate Email Confirmation Token
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Tokens/email-confirmation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "userId": "{{login.response.body.$.userId}}"
}

###

### Generate Password Reset Token
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Tokens/password-reset
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "userId": "{{login.response.body.$.userId}}"
}

###

### Reset Password
POST {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/api/Tokens/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_Token}}

{
  "userId": "{{login.response.body.$.userId}}",
  "token": "reset_token_here",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123!"
}

###

# Weather Forecast (No Authentication Required)
GET {{GoodHamburger.Api_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

